                        <br/><br/><br/><h2>文 献</h2><br><ol><br><li id="R1"><span class='au'>La Spada, A. R., Wilson, E. M., Lubahn, D. B. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">Androgen receptor gene mutations in X-linked spinal and bulbar muscular atrophy.</span> <span class='so'>Nature, 352, 77-79 (1991)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/2062380" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R2"><span class='au'>Kennedy, W. R., Alter, M. & Sung, J. H.</span>: <span class="ti">Progressive proximal spinal and bulbar muscular atrophy of late onset: a sex-linked recessive trait.</span> <span class='so'>Neurology, 50, 583-593 (1998)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9521237" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R3"><span class='au'>Sobue, G., Hashizume, Y., Mukai, E. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">X-linked recessive bulbospinal neuronopathy. A clinicopathological study.</span> <span class='so'>Brain, 112, 209-232 (1989)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/2917278" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R4"><span class='au'>Kim, V. N., Han, J. & Siomi, M. C.</span>: <span class="ti">Biogenesis of small RNAs in animals.</span> <span class='so'>Nat. Rev. Mol. Cell Biol., 10, 126-139 (2009)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19165215" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R5"><span class='au'>Kim, J., Inoue, K., Ishii, J. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">A microRNA feedback circuit in midbrain dopamine neurons.</span> <span class='so'>Science, 317, 1220-1224 (2007)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/17761882" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R6"><span class='au'>Karres, J. S., Hilgers, V., Carrera, I. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">The conserved microRNA miR-8 tunes atrophin levels to prevent neurodegeneration in <em>Drosophila</em>.</span> <span class='so'>Cell, 131, 136-145 (2007)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/17923093" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></l